                         <heading>Roads</heading>
                         <p id="AL.DIR.331">A highway linking Tirana and Vlorë was completed in 2006, and a highway linking Durrës with Kosovo was completed in 2010. Construction of the Arbër highway, linking Albania with North Macedonia, commenced in mid-2018, and was part-opened in November 2021.</p>
